description:
Take a look onboard the World's most Luxurious First Class plane ticket... Emirates Gamechanger First Class.

Operated on just a few planes (the Boeing 777-300ER) with routes changing all the time it can be difficult to get onboard one of these uber exclusive suites. Today i'm lifting the veil on this super exclusive plane seat, what's it like to fly, how much does it cost and how can you do the same?
